beer.beer_description:
Forager is a New England IPA packed full of luscious home grown hops from Australia – Galaxy & Vic Secret - in combination with world-class kiwi cones – Nelson Sauvin & Riwaka. A heavy dry hop of 24g/L sits on top a base of soft water and Multi-Stacked Oats™,  fermented out with a no frills London Ale III yeast. 
Brewed in collaboration with our long time pals at Gipsy Hill Brewing Company in London, UK as part of a home and away series.
